# Iron age

**Oh, you meant the [Iron Age](/Iron_Age)? Obviously.**

This page exists because someone, somewhere, typed "Iron age" instead of "[Iron Age](/Iron_Age)" and the internet just sighed deeply. It's a redirect—a digital correction slip for people who apparently struggle with the shift key. How thrilling.

